# VFIDE Frontend Design System: VFIDE Meets Future
**Version**: 1.0  
**Theme**: Medieval Crusader + Cyberpunk/Sci-Fi  
**Philosophy**: "Ancient honor, future tech"  
**Date**: December 3, 2025  

---

## 1. Design Philosophy

### 1.1 Core Concept
**"The New VFIDE protecting digital commerce"**

The VFIDE were medieval warrior-monks who invented banking, protected pilgrims, and created the first international financial system. VFIDE merchants are the **modern Templars** - protecting buyers with ProofScore, creating trust in decentralized commerce.

**Visual Identity**:
- **Medieval Elements**: Red cross (Templar symbol), Gothic typography, stone/chainmail textures, heraldic shields, wax seals, ancient scrolls
- **Futuristic Elements**: Neon accents, holographic effects, digital HUDs, glowing lines, particle effects, cyber grids, matrix-style data streams

**Color Philosophy**:
- Primary: **Primary Red** (#C41E3A) - Honor, blood oath, commitment
- Secondary: **Cyber Blue** (#00F0FF) - Technology, trust, future
- Accent: **Gold** (#FFD700) - Wealth, ProofScore achievement, elite status
- Background: **Dark Stone** (#1A1A1D) - Medieval castle walls, space black
- Neutral: **Steel Gray** (#4A4A4F) - Chainmail, metal armor

---

## 2. Complete VFIDE Ecosystem Modules

### 2.1 Core Contracts Mapped to Frontend Features

| Smart Contract | Frontend Module | User-Facing Feature |
|----------------|-----------------|---------------------|
| **VFIDEToken.sol** | Token Dashboard | Balance, burns, transfers |
| **ProofScoreBurnRouter.sol** | ProofScore System | Score display, tier badges, burn tracking |
| **VFIDETrust.sol** (Seer) | Trust Explorer | Reputation lookup, endorsements, disputes |
| **MerchantPortal.sol** | Merchant Dashboard | Payments, analytics, settings |
| **EscrowManager.sol** | Escrow Interface | Active escrows, release, disputes |
| **VaultInfrastructure.sol** | Vault Manager | Create vault, deposit, withdraw, lock |
| **GuardianNodeSale.sol** | Guardian Marketplace | Buy nodes, track investment, claim rewards |
| **DAOTimelockV2.sol** | Governance Portal | Vote on proposals, view timelock queue |
| **CouncilElection.sol** | Council Voting | Elect guardians, view candidates |
| **RevenueSplitter.sol** | Treasury View | Revenue distribution, fee tracking |
| **VFIDECommerce.sol** | Checkout Page | Payment processing, ProofScore display |
| **VFIDEFinance.sol** | Finance Dashboard | DAO budget, spending, reserves |
| **DevReserveVestingVault.sol** | Vesting Tracker | Dev team vesting schedule |
| **MerchantRebateVault.sol** | Rebate Tracker | Ecosystem fees, merchant rebates |
| **SubscriptionManager.sol** | Subscription Portal | Recurring payments, manage subscriptions |
| **EmergencyControl.sol** | Emergency Panel | Pause/unpause, emergency actions (admin only) |
| **SystemHandover.sol** | Decentralization Timeline | Countdown to full DAO control |

