## 4. Design System Components

### 4.1 Typography

**Primary Font**: **"Cinzel"** (Google Fonts)
- Medieval-inspired serif for headers
- Evokes ancient Roman inscriptions, Templar manuscripts
- Weight: 700 (Bold) for titles, 400 (Regular) for body

**Secondary Font**: **"Orbitron"** (Google Fonts)
- Futuristic geometric sans-serif for UI elements
- Used for: Numbers, data, buttons, labels
- Weight: 900 (Black) for emphasis, 400 (Regular) for body

**Code Font**: **"Fira Code"** (Google Fonts)
- Monospace for wallet addresses, transaction hashes
- Ligatures enabled for arrows (->), equals (==)

**Example**:
```css
/* Headers: Medieval */
h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #C41E3A; /* Primary Red */
  text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(196, 30, 58, 0.5);
}

/* UI Text: Futuristic */
button, label, .ui-text {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}

/* Data: Monospace */
.address, .hash, code {
  font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
  color: #00F0FF; /* Cyber Blue */
  background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
  padding: 2px 6px;
  border-radius: 3px;
}
```

---

### 4.2 Color Palette

| Color Name | Hex | Usage | Templar Element | Future Element |
|------------|-----|-------|----------------|----------------|
| **Primary Red** | #C41E3A | Primary CTA, ProofScore 751+ | Red cross, blood oath | Danger alerts, important |
| **Cyber Blue** | #00F0FF | Interactive elements, links | - | Holograms, neon glow |
| **Gold** | #FFD700 | Elite badges, achievements | Treasure, wealth, honor | Premium features |
| **Dark Stone** | #1A1A1D | Background, panels | Castle walls, night | Space black, void |
| **Steel Gray** | #4A4A4F | Borders, dividers, text | Chainmail, armor | Metal, chrome |
| **White Parchment** | #F5F3E8 | Text on dark bg | Ancient scrolls | Holographic text |
| **Emerald Green** | #50C878 | Success states | - | Matrix green, active |
| **Blood Orange** | #FF4500 | Warnings, disputes | - | Alert, danger |

**Gradient Examples**:
```css
/* Cross Symbol Glow */
