### 4.3 ProofScore Tier System (Visual Design)

| Tier | Score Range | Badge | Color | Icon | Title |
|------|------------|-------|-------|------|-------|
| **Squire** | 0-500 | ![](squire.svg) | Steel Gray | 🛡️ | "Apprentice Merchant" |
| **Knight** | 501-750 | ![](knight.svg) | Cyber Blue | ⚔️ | "Trusted Knight" |
| **Elite** | 751-900 | ![](elite.svg) | Gold | 🏆 | "Elite Commander" |
| **Templar** | 901-1000 | ![](templar.svg) | Primary Red | 👑 | "Grand Master Templar" |

**Badge Design**:
- **Squire**: Simple shield outline, no fill
- **Knight**: Shield with cross, blue glow
- **Elite**: Shield with cross, gold glow, particle effects
- **Templar**: Ornate shield, red glow, animated particles, crown above

**CSS Example**:
```css
.proofscore-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.proofscore-badge.squire {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A4A4F 0%, #6A6A6F 100%);
  color: #F5F3E8;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(74, 74, 79, 0.4);
}

.proofscore-badge.knight {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00F0FF 0%, #0080FF 100%);
  color: #1A1A1D;
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.6);
}

.proofscore-badge.elite {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700 0%, #FFA500 100%);
  color: #1A1A1D;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8);
  animation: pulse-gold 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.proofscore-badge.templar {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C41E3A 0%, #FF4500 100%);
  color: #F5F3E8;
  box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(196, 30, 58, 1);
  animation: pulse-red 1s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes glow {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes pulse-gold {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
}

@keyframes pulse-red {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.08) rotate(1deg); }
}
```

