### 4.4 Button Styles

**Primary Button** (Cross Symbol):
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C41E3A 0%, #FF4500 100%);
  border: 2px solid #FFD700;
  color: #F5F3E8;
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 12px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(196, 30, 58, 0.6);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.btn-primary::before {
  content: '⚔️';
  position: absolute;
  left: 12px;
  font-size: 20px;
  animation: sword-strike 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(196, 30, 58, 1);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

@keyframes sword-strike {
  0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  50% { transform: rotate(10deg); }
}
```

**Secondary Button** (Cyber):
```css
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid #00F0FF;
  color: #00F0FF;
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  padding: 12px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
  background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.6);
}
```

