### 4.5 Card/Panel Component

**Merchant Dashboard Card**:
```jsx
// components/TemplarCard.tsx
export function TemplarCard({ title, children, tier = "knight" }) {
  return (
    <div className="templar-card" data-tier={tier}>
      <div className="card-header">
        <h3>{title}</h3>
        <div className="corner-ornament">⚔️</div>
      </div>
      <div className="card-body">
        {children}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

```css
/* TemplarCard.css */
.templar-card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A1D 0%, #2A2A2F 100%);
  border: 2px solid #4A4A4F;
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  padding: 24px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.templar-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
    #C41E3A 0%, 
    #00F0FF 50%, 
    #C41E3A 100%);
  animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.card-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding-bottom: 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
}

.card-header h3 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  color: #F5F3E8;
  margin: 0;
}

.corner-ornament {
  font-size: 24px;
  opacity: 0.5;
  animation: float 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes shimmer {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
}
```

