## 6. Technical Implementation Plan

### 6.1 Tech Stack (Unified Across All Sites)

**Frontend Framework**:
- **Next.js 14** (App Router) - merchant, pay, explorer
- **Astro** (static) - marketing site (vfide.com)

**Web3 Integration**:
- **wagmi v2** (React hooks for Ethereum)
- **viem** (TypeScript-native Ethereum library)
- **RainbowKit** (wallet connection UI - customized with Professional theme)

**UI/Styling**:
- **Tailwind CSS** (utility-first)
- **Framer Motion** (animations)
- **Three.js** (3D graphics - Templar cross, particle effects)
- **GSAP** (scroll animations)
- **Lottie** (micro-animations - icons, loaders)

**State Management**:
- **Zustand** (lightweight state)
- **React Query** (data fetching, caching)

**Database**:
- **Supabase** (PostgreSQL, auth, realtime)

**Hosting**:
- **Vercel** (Next.js sites)
- **Cloudflare Pages** (Astro marketing site)

